result.execSummary:
The defendant Ashley Vasquez was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Ashley Vasquez is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Ashley Vasquez was found guilty of Possession of Narcotic Drugs, a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(am).
